<body>

  <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

  <main class="container py-5">
    <div class="info-card">
      <h1 class="gfn-title mb-4">About GFN Games</h1>

      <p>GFN Games is a clean, fast browser for the full GeForce NOW game catalog. Find out which games you can stream directly via NVIDIA's cloud gaming service.</p>

